milestones.description: Wessels's 90 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for SA), surpassing Wessels's 71
Wessels has broken the record for most runs in boundaries (40) in an innings in ODIs for SA, going past Wessels's 24
Wessels and Jimmy Cook's 72-run partnership is SA's highest for the 1st wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 3 between Andrew Hudson and Jimmy Cook
Wessels and Peter Kirsten's 111-run partnership is SA's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 94 between Wessels and Mandy Yachad
Peter Kirsten and Adrian Kuiper's 105-run partnership is SA's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 21 between Wessels and Peter Kirsten
Ravi Shastri and Manjrekar's 175-run partnership is IND's highest for the 2nd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 165 between Gavaskar and Azharuddin
Richard Snell has conceded the most runs in an innings (56) in ODIs for SA, going past Tim Shaw's record of 46
McMillan has broken the record for most catches (2) in ODIs for SA, going past Clive Eksteen's 1
This is the highest match aggregate (575) involving teams South Africa & India in ODIs
Wessels and Peter Kirsten's 111-run partnership is SA's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 94 between Mandy Yachad and Wessels
Jimmy Cook has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (3) for SA, going past Allan Donald
